      • AbstractElement

        protected AbstractElement()
        Constructor to use to represent a root element. A root element has an id of -1.

      • AbstractElement

        protected AbstractElement(java.lang.String name,
                          AbstractElement parent)
        Constructor to use to represent a non-root element.
        参数:
        name - name for this element (required, cannot be "/")
        parent - for this element (required, cannot be null)
